<hex:022B7EFF7C><hex:020825E1E93501FF1D><hex:022819FF14>GCRankLimsaMaleText<hex:E9350903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020828E1E93601FF20><hex:02281CFF17>GCRankGridaniaMaleText<hex:E9360903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020825E1E93701FF1D><hex:022819FF14>GCRankUldahMaleText<hex:E9370903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:03> <hex:022C0DFF07><hex:022903EB0203><hex:FF02> <hex:0303>! While I am certain that your duties with <hex:020816E1E93501FF0E>the Maelstrom<hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020824E1E93601FF1C>the Order of the Twin Adder<hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:02081CE1E93701FF14>the Immortal Flames<hex:FF01><hex:03> demand much of your time already, I wondered if I might have a word?

I shall get right to the point, <hex:022B7EFF7C><hex:020825E1E93501FF1D><hex:022819FF14>GCRankLimsaMaleText<hex:E9350903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020828E1E93601FF20><hex:02281CFF17>GCRankGridaniaMaleText<hex:E9360903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020825E1E93701FF1D><hex:022819FF14>GCRankUldahMaleText<hex:E9370903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:03>. The higher-ups have authorized plans to form a specialized squad and we are on the lookout for a reliable leader. Your name was at the top of the list.

You would be responsible for training and commanding a number of adventurer subordinates, and the position also comes with the possibility of further promotion. What say you, <hex:022B7EFF7C><hex:020825E1E93501FF1D><hex:022819FF14>GCRankLimsaMaleText<hex:E9350903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020828E1E93601FF20><hex:02281CFF17>GCRankGridaniaMaleText<hex:E9360903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020825E1E93701FF1D><hex:022819FF14>GCRankUldahMaleText<hex:E9370903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:03>? Are you ready to lead?
（★未使用／削除予定★）
（★未使用／削除予定★）
Become a squadron commander?
Yes
No
Ah. Well, 'tis hardly the response I was hoping for, but 'tis best we are all honest here. A hesitant commander is a danger to <hex:02080DE905FF04>her<hex:FF04>his<hex:03> own troops.
Excellent! Let's get you acquainted with your second-in-command immediately.

It's an honor to be serving with you, <hex:022B7EFF7C><hex:020825E1E93501FF1D><hex:022819FF14>GCRankLimsaMaleText<hex:E9350903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020828E1E93601FF20><hex:02281CFF17>GCRankGridaniaMaleText<hex:E9360903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020825E1E93701FF1D><hex:022819FF14>GCRankUldahMaleText<hex:E9370903><hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:03> <hex:022C0DFF07><hex:022903EB0203><hex:FF02> <hex:0303>! In my capacity as your aide, I'll be filling the role of squadron sergeant.
And these eager troopers are the inaugural members of our squadron. Form up!
Every one of them is a fledgling adventurer who enlisted in the hopes of following in your legendary footsteps. They're green to the military, aye, but we'll harden them up soon enough.
When you've a moment to spare, stop by the barracks and we can discuss their training and deployment in greater detail.
I'll leave you to it, then, Commander.
What do you think? I must admit they're raw as soldiers go, but they certainly have potential. I look forward to seeing what you can do with them.

Very well, I shan't keep you any longer. Your squadron's barracks can be found through the door at the back of the <hex:020815E1E93501FF0D>command room<hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020815E1E93601FF0D>Adders' Nest<hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020817E1E93701FF0F>Hall of Flames<hex:FF01><hex:03>.

May <hex:02082BE1E93501FF23>the Navigator guide you to victory<hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020822E1E93601FF1A>the Matron watch over you<hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020829E1E93701FF21>Nald'thal bless you with fortune<hex:FF01><hex:03>!

You are now the commander of an adventurer squadron!<hex:02100103>Enter the <hex:020812E1E93501FF0A>Maelstrom<hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:020813E1E93601FF0B>Twin Adder<hex:FF01><hex:03><hex:02080EE1E93701FF06>Flame<hex:FF01><hex:03> Barracks and speak with your squadron sergeant to issue deployment orders.
